## 3. Performance & ship rules
- **60 FPS @ 1080p** on GTX 1060 ‚Äî test SC-02 Ruined Village vertical slice first.
- **‚â§ 8 materials** visible per zone at gameplay camera.
- Log third-party assets in `docs/art/LICENSES.md`; run `bash tools/check_asset_compliance.sh` before commit.
- Godot scenes/scripts for **Phases 1‚Äì6 gameplay** may land on `main` per `docs/workflow/IMPLEMENTATION_PLAN.md` or on feature branches ‚Äî either is OK if PR-reviewed
- `main` always holds: design docs, `game/data/` JSON, boot shell, validators, and story stubs (`CinematicDirector`, `VoiceLinePlayer`)

